}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== This device has the same board ID as the [[Belkin F5D7633-4]] and [[Belkin F5D7631-4 v2]]. This router may be known as the [http://cache-www.belkin.com/support/dl/p75125uk_f5d9630uk4a.pdf F5D9630-4A] overseas.
The default SSID is assumed to be '''Belkin_G_Plus_MIMO_ADSL'''.
